column2: "Oh!! Great timing! Help me out!"
"Someone's coming! Keep her busy, 'kay? I'm counting on you!"
"<%me>? What are you doing here?"
"...I uh, was asked to meet someone else..."
"H-hey, Azanami!! Why are you pushing me over here!?"
"Keep moving and you'll find out soon.\u3000And... ta-dah!"
"Just what on earth are you--"
"W-wait!"
"What..?"
"I don't mind if you hate me. That is your right."
"But please, tell me if I have wronged you in any way."
"I'm certain I have offended you somehow. I need to know, as I am oblivious to such things."
"Please. So I can apologize properly."
"...No, it was me who misunderstood, and intentionally avoided you."
"...I need to apologize, not you. But... I'm not as brave as you."
"...All I did was keep my distance."
"...You did nothing wrong. The fault is mine alone."
"<%me>, thanks for the assist!"
"All's well that end's well! Let's leave the rest to them, eh?"
